WHO   — Baron Vladimir Harkonnen — the grotesque architect of the Atreides fall
WHAT  — The brilliant and monstrous ruler of House Harkonnen, who engineers the destruction of House Atreides.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: House Harkonnen — the fall of the Atreides on Arrakis  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
